<mjml>
  <mj-head>
    <mj-preview></mj-preview>
    <mj-breakpoint width="480px"></mj-breakpoint>
    <mj-attributes>
      <mj-all padding="0"></mj-all>
    </mj-attributes>
    <mj-style>
      @media only screen and (max-width: 799px) {
        .text > div {
            text-align: inherit !important;
        }
    
        .wrapper > table > tbody > tr > td {
            padding-left: 0px !important;
            padding-right: 0px !important;
        }

        .section > table > tbody > tr > td {
            padding-left: 20px !important;
            padding-right: 20px !important;
        }

        .column > table > tbody > tr > td {
            padding-left: 0px !important;
            padding-right: 0px !important;
        }

        .padB40 {
            padding-bottom: 40px !important;
        }

        .image {
            padding-left: 0px !important;
            padding-right: 0px !important;
        }

        .image > table {
            text-align: center !important;
            margin: 0 auto !important;
        }

        .divider {
            padding-left: 0px !important;
            padding-right: 0px !important;
        }

        .button > table {
            width: 100% !important;
        }

        .button > table > tbody > tr > td > a {
            width: 80% !important;
        }
    }
    </mj-style>
    <mj-style inline="inline">
      .column > table { border-collapse: separate; }
    </mj-style>
    <mj-font href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=DM+Sans:wght@400&display=swap" name="DM Sans"></mj-font>
    <mj-font href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Public+Sans:wght@700&display=swap" name="Public Sans"></mj-font>
  </mj-head>
  <mj-body background-color="#f5f5fe" name="Candidature spontanée" width="800px">
    <mj-wrapper border-radius="0px" css-class="wrapper" padding="32px 100px 32px 100px">
      <mj-section border-radius="0px" css-class="section" name="mj-section_group">
        <mj-group>
          <mj-column border-radius="0px" css-class="column" vertical-align="middle" width="14.83%">
            <mj-image align="left" alt="Image" css-class="image" src="<%= data.images.logoRF %>" width="89px"></mj-image>
          </mj-column>
          <mj-column border-radius="0px" css-class="column" padding="0px 24px 0px 24px" vertical-align="middle" width="34.83%">
            <mj-image align="left" alt="Image" css-class="image" padding="17px 0px 17px 0px" src="<%= data.images.logoLba %>" width="160px"></mj-image>
          </mj-column>
          <mj-column border-radius="0px" css-class="column" vertical-align="top" width="50.33%"></mj-column>
        </mj-group>
      </mj-section>
      <mj-spacer height="24px"></mj-spacer>
      <mj-section background-color="#ffffff" border-radius="4px" border="1px solid #e3e3fd" css-class="section" name="mj-section_group" padding="23px 23px 23px 23px">
        <mj-group>
          <mj-column border-radius="0px" css-class="column" padding="0px 0px 0px 0px" vertical-align="middle" width="33.03%">
            <mj-image align="center" alt="Image" css-class="image" padding="2px 0px 2px 0px" src="<%= data.images.recuCandidature %>" width="183px"></mj-image>
          </mj-column>
          <mj-column css-class="padB40" width="4.7%">
            <mj-spacer height="0px"></mj-spacer>
          </mj-column>
          <mj-column border-radius="0px" css-class="column" vertical-align="middle" width="62.27%">
            <mj-text align="left" color="#161616" css-class="text" font-family="DM Sans, Times, Georgia, serif" font-size="14px" font-weight="400" line-height="24px">
              <a href="https://labonnealternance.apprentissage.beta.gouv.fr?&utm_source=jecandidate&utm_medium=email&utm_campaign=jecandidaterecruteur" style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, Verdana, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; text-decoration: underline; color: inherit;">La bonne alternance</a><span style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, Verdana, sans-serif; font-weight: 400;"> est un service public qui vise à favoriser les entrées en alternance. Votre entreprise </span><span style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, Verdana, sans-serif; font-weight: 700; color: #161616;"><%= data.company_name %></span><span style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, Verdana, sans-serif; font-weight: 400;"> a été identifiée comme “à fort potentiel d’embauche” sur la base de données publiques. Les candidats peuvent vous soumettre leur candidature via notre plateforme et nos sites partenaires dont 1jeune1solution et Parcoursup.</span>
<br/>
            </mj-text>
          </mj-column>
        </mj-group>
      </mj-section>
      <mj-spacer height="24px"></mj-spacer>
      <mj-section background-color="#ffffff" border-radius="4px" border="1px solid #e3e3fd" css-class="section" name="mj-section_group" padding="23px 23px 23px 23px">
        <mj-group>
          <mj-column border-radius="0px" css-class="column" vertical-align="middle" width="99.64%">
            <mj-text align="left" color="#161616" css-class="text" font-family="Arial, Helvetica, Verdana, sans-serif" font-size="16px" font-weight="400" line-height="24px" padding="0px 0px 16px 0px">
              <span style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 28px; font-weight: 700; color: #161616;"><%= data.applicant_first_name %> <%= data.applicant_last_name %></span><span style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, Verdana, sans-serif; line-height: 28px; font-weight: 400;"> s'intéresse à </span><span style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 28px; font-weight: 400; color: #161616;">votre entreprise</span><span style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, Verdana, sans-serif; line-height: 28px; font-weight: 400;"> et vous adresse sa candidature spontanée.</span>
<br/>
            </mj-text>
            <mj-text align="left" color="#161616" css-class="text" font-family="Arial, Helvetica, Verdana, sans-serif" font-size="16px" font-weight="400" line-height="28px" padding="0px 0px 16px 0px">
              Nous vous invitons à prendre connaissance de sa candidature ci-dessous avant de lui répondre en quelques clics à l'aide des boutons suivants :
<br/>
            </mj-text>
            <mj-button href="<%= data.meetCandidateUrl %>" align="center" background-color="#18753c" border-radius="0px" color="#ffffff" css-class="button" font-family="Arial, Helvetica, Verdana, sans-serif" font-size="14px" font-weight="700" inner-padding="4px 0px 4px 0px" line-height="24px" padding="0px 0px 16px 0px" width="184px">
              Rencontrer le candidat
            </mj-button>
            <mj-button href="<%= data.waitCandidateUrl %>" align="center" background-color="#000091" border-radius="0px" color="#ffffff" css-class="button" font-family="Arial, Helvetica, Verdana, sans-serif" font-size="14px" font-weight="700" inner-padding="4px 0px 4px 0px" line-height="24px" padding="0px 0px 16px 0px" width="181px">
              En attente de décision
            </mj-button>
            <mj-button href="<%= data.refuseCandidateUrl %>" align="center" background-color="#ce0500" border-radius="0px" color="#ffffff" css-class="button" font-family="Arial, Helvetica, Verdana, sans-serif" font-size="14px" font-weight="700" inner-padding="4px 0px 4px 0px" line-height="24px" padding="0px 0px 16px 0px" width="184px">
              Refuser la candidature
            </mj-button>
            <mj-text align="center" color="#161616" css-class="text" font-family="Arial, Helvetica, Verdana, sans-serif" font-size="14px" font-weight="400" line-height="24px" padding="0px 0px 16px 0px" text-decoration="underline">
              <a href="<%= data.unsubscribeUrl %>" style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, Verdana, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; text-decoration: underline; color: inherit;">
                🚫 Je ne souhaite plus recevoir de candidature spontanée
              </a>
<br/>
            </mj-text>
            <mj-text align="left" color="#666666" css-class="text" font-family="Arial, Helvetica, Verdana, sans-serif" font-size="14px" font-weight="400" line-height="24px">
              Ce courriel est généré automatiquement, vous ne pouvez pas y répondre.
<br/>Pour répondre au candidat, veuillez utiliser les boutons de réponse situés ci-dessus.
<br/>
            </mj-text>
          </mj-column>
        </mj-group>
      </mj-section>
      <mj-spacer height="24px"></mj-spacer>
      <mj-section background-color="#ffffff" border-radius="4px" border="1px solid #e3e3fd" css-class="section" name="mj-section_group" padding="23px 23px 23px 23px">
        <mj-group>
          <mj-column border-radius="0px" css-class="column" vertical-align="middle" width="-497.84000000000003%">
            <mj-text align="left" color="#000091" css-class="text" font-family="Arial, Helvetica, Verdana, sans-serif" font-size="20px" font-weight="700" line-height="22px">
              Candidature
<br/>
            </mj-text>
          </mj-column>
          <mj-spacer height="24px" padding="0px 24px 0px 24px"></mj-spacer>
          <mj-column border-radius="0px" css-class="column" padding="0px 0px 0px 0px" vertical-align="middle" width="99.64%">
            <mj-text align="left" color="#161616" css-class="text" font-family="Arial, Helvetica, Verdana, sans-serif" font-size="16px" font-weight="400" line-height="24px" padding="4px 0px 0px 0px">
              Nom : 
<br/>
            </mj-text>
            <mj-text align="left" color="#161616" css-class="text" font-family="Arial, Helvetica, Verdana, sans-serif" font-size="16px" font-weight="700" line-height="24px" padding="0px 0px 4px 0px">
              <%= data.applicant_last_name %>
<br/>
            </mj-text>
          </mj-column>
          <mj-spacer height="24px" padding="0px 24px 0px 24px"></mj-spacer>
          <mj-column border-radius="0px" css-class="column" padding="0px 0px 0px 0px" vertical-align="middle" width="99.64%">
            <mj-text align="left" color="#161616" css-class="text" font-family="Arial, Helvetica, Verdana, sans-serif" font-size="16px" font-weight="400" line-height="24px" padding="4px 0px 0px 0px">
              Prénom :
<br/>
            </mj-text>
            <mj-text align="left" color="#161616" css-class="text" font-family="Arial, Helvetica, Verdana, sans-serif" font-size="16px" font-weight="700" line-height="24px" padding="0px 0px 4px 0px">
              <%= data.applicant_first_name %>
<br/>
            </mj-text>
          </mj-column>
          <mj-spacer height="24px" padding="0px 24px 0px 24px"></mj-spacer>
          <mj-column border-radius="0px" css-class="column" vertical-align="middle" width="99.64%">
            <mj-text align="left" color="#161616" css-class="text" font-family="Arial, Helvetica, Verdana, sans-serif" font-size="16px" font-weight="400" line-height="24px">
              Téléphone :
<br/>
            </mj-text>
            <mj-text align="left" color="#161616" css-class="text" font-family="Arial, Helvetica, Verdana, sans-serif" font-size="16px" font-weight="700" line-height="24px">
              <%= data.applicant_phone %>
<br/>
            </mj-text>
          </mj-column>
          <mj-spacer height="24px" padding="0px 24px 0px 24px"></mj-spacer>
          <mj-column border-radius="0px" css-class="column" vertical-align="middle" width="99.64%">
            <mj-text align="left" color="#161616" css-class="text" font-family="Arial, Helvetica, Verdana, sans-serif" font-size="16px" font-weight="400" line-height="24px">
              E-mail :
<br/>
            </mj-text>
            <mj-text align="left" color="#000091" css-class="text" font-family="Arial, Helvetica, Verdana, sans-serif" font-size="16px" font-weight="700" line-height="24px" text-decoration="underline">
              <a href="mailto:<%= data.applicant_email %>" style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, Verdana, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; text-decoration: underline; color: inherit;">
                <%= data.applicant_email %>
              </a>
<br/>
            </mj-text>
          </mj-column>
          <mj-column border-radius="0px" css-class="column" padding="0px 0px 0px 0px" vertical-align="middle" width="99.64%">
            <mj-text align="left" color="#161616" css-class="text" font-family="Arial, Helvetica, Verdana, sans-serif" font-size="14px" font-style="italic" font-weight="400" line-height="16px" padding="20px 0px 20px 0px">
              Vous trouverez le curriculum vitae du candidat en pièce jointe. 
<br/>
            </mj-text>
          </mj-column>
          <% if (data.applicant_message_to_company) { %>
          <mj-column border-radius="0px" css-class="column" vertical-align="middle" width="99.64%">
            <mj-text align="left" color="#161616" css-class="text" font-family="Arial, Helvetica, Verdana, sans-serif" font-size="16px" font-weight="400" line-height="24px">
              Message du candidat : 
<br/>
            </mj-text>
            <mj-text align="left" color="#161616" css-class="text" font-family="Arial, Helvetica, Verdana, sans-serif" font-size="16px" font-weight="700" line-height="28px">
              <%= data.applicant_message_to_company %>
<br/>
            </mj-text>
          </mj-column>
          <% } %>
        </mj-group>
      </mj-section>
      <mj-spacer height="24px"></mj-spacer>
      <mj-section background-color="#ffffff" border-radius="4px" border="1px solid #e3e3fd" css-class="section" name="mj-section_group" padding="11px 23px 11px 23px">
        <mj-group>
          <mj-column border-radius="0px" css-class="column" padding="0px 0px 0px 0px" vertical-align="middle" width="100%">
            <mj-text align="left" color="#000091" css-class="text" font-family="Arial, Helvetica, Verdana, sans-serif" font-size="20px" font-weight="700" line-height="22px" padding="10px 0px 10px 0px">
              <span style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, Verdana, sans-serif; font-weight: 400;">🎲 </span>Préparez l'arrivée de votre futur·e alternant·e
<br/>
            </mj-text>
          </mj-column>
          <mj-column border-radius="0px" css-class="column" padding="0px 0px 0px 0px" vertical-align="middle" width="99.64%">
            <mj-text align="left" color="#161616" css-class="text" font-family="Arial, Helvetica, Verdana, sans-serif" font-size="16px" font-weight="400" line-height="28px" padding="10px 0px 10px 0px">
              Vous recrutez un·e alternant·e ? On vous accompagne dans les étapes clés de son intégration <a href="https://dinum.didask.com/courses/lalternance-pour-les-recruteurs" style="text-decoration: underline; color: inherit;">grâce à ce quiz interactif de 7 questions</a>.
<br/>
            </mj-text>
          </mj-column>
        </mj-group>
      </mj-section>
      <mj-spacer height="24px"></mj-spacer>
      <mj-section background-color="#ffffff" border-radius="4px" border="1px solid #e3e3fd" css-class="section" name="mj-section_group" padding="23px 23px 23px 23px">
        <mj-group>
          <mj-column border-radius="0px" css-class="column" vertical-align="middle" width="99.64%">
            <mj-text align="left" color="#000091" css-class="text" font-family="Arial, Helvetica, Verdana, sans-serif" font-size="20px" font-weight="700" line-height="22px" padding="0px 0px 12px 0px">
              Une question ?
<br/>
            </mj-text>
            <mj-text align="left" color="#161616" css-class="text" font-family="Arial, Helvetica, Verdana, sans-serif" font-size="14px" font-weight="400" line-height="24px" padding="0px 0px 12px 0px" text-decoration="underline">
              <a href="<%= data.unsubscribeUrl %>" style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, Verdana, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; text-decoration: underline; color: inherit;">
              🚫 Déréférencer mon établissement
              </a>
              <br/>
            </mj-text>
            <mj-text align="left" color="#161616" css-class="text" font-family="Arial, Helvetica, Verdana, sans-serif" font-size="14px" font-weight="400" line-height="24px" padding="0px 0px 12px 0px" text-decoration="underline">
              <a href="mailto:labonnealternance@apprentissage.beta.gouv.fr?subject=MAJ%20informations%20entreprise%20-%20Candidature%20spontanée" style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, Verdana, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; text-decoration: underline; color: inherit;">
                📝 Modifier les données de mon établissement"
              </a>
<br/>
            </mj-text>
            <mj-text  align="left" color="#161616" css-class="text" font-family="Marianne, sans-serif" font-size="14px" font-weight="400" line-height="24px" padding="0px 0px 12px 0px" text-decoration="underline">
              <a href="<%= data.lbaRecruiterUrl %>" style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, Verdana, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; text-decoration: underline; color: inherit;">
                <span style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, Verdana, sans-serif; font-weight: 400;">🚀 </span><span style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, Verdana, sans-serif; font-weight: 400;">
                  Diffuser simplement et gratuitement une offre en alternance
                </span>
              </a>
<br/>
            </mj-text>
            <mj-text align="left" color="#161616" css-class="text" font-family="Marianne, sans-serif" font-size="14px" font-weight="400" line-height="24px" text-decoration="underline">
              <span style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, Verdana, sans-serif; font-weight: 400;">💬</span>&nbsp;<a href="<%= data.faqUrl %>" style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, Verdana, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; text-decoration: underline; color: inherit;">Consulter la FAQ</a>
<br/>
            </mj-text>
          </mj-column>
        </mj-group>
      </mj-section>
      <mj-spacer height="24px"></mj-spacer>
      <mj-section border-radius="4px" css-class="section" name="mj-section_group">
        <mj-group>
          <mj-column border-radius="0px" css-class="column" vertical-align="middle" width="100%">
            <mj-text align="left" color="#666666" css-class="text" font-family="Arial, Helvetica, Verdana, sans-serif" font-size="14px" font-weight="400" line-height="24px">
              La bonne alternance est un site développé par la Mission interministérielle pour l'apprentissage, au sein de l’État, conformément aux missions d’intérêt public du ministère du Travail, du Plein emploi et de l’Insertion.
<br/>Vous recevez cette candidature car nous avons identifié votre entreprise comme étant susceptible de recruter en alternance et nous avons utilisé l’email que vous avez déclaré dans votre espace recruteur France Travail.
<br/>
<br/>Nous vous contactons car nous souhaitons vous proposer des candidats à l'alternance.
<br/>
<br/>Nous ne faisons aucune utilisation commerciale de vos adresses e-mail. Vous bénéficiez d’un droit d’opposition que vous pouvez utiliser à tout moment via l’adresse <a href="mailto:labonnealternance@apprentissage.beta.gouv.fr?subject=Droit%20opposition" style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, Verdana, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; text-decoration: underline; color: inherit;">labonnealternance@apprentissage.beta.gouv.fr</a>
<br/>
<br/>Si vos droits ne sont pas respectés, vous pouvez à tout moment introduire une réclamation auprès de la CNIL. Pour plus d’informations sur le traitement de vos données, vous pouvez vous rendre sur la <a href="https://labonnealternance.apprentissage.beta.gouv.fr/politique-de-confidentialite" style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, Verdana, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; text-decoration: underline; color: inherit;">politique de confidentialité</a> de La bonne alternance.
<br/>
            </mj-text>
          </mj-column>
        </mj-group>
      </mj-section>
    </mj-wrapper>
  </mj-body>
</mjml>
